# The Hand of the King — schedule
#
# Install with: crontab -e   (then paste the lines below)
# Or:           crontab ~/Kingdom/council/the-hand-of-the-king/cron.example
#
# Times are in the server's local timezone. If the server is UTC,
# 04:00 UTC = 06:00 CAT (Africa/Johannesburg, UTC+2).
# Confirm with: timedatectl  | grep "Time zone"
# If the server is already on Africa/Johannesburg, change "0 4" to "0 6".

# Daily 06:00 CAT — morning brief to the king's Telegram
# (assumes UTC server)
0 4 * * * /home/lauchlandupreez/Kingdom/bin/hand telegram >> /home/lauchlandupreez/Kingdom/.hand-cron.log 2>&1

# Every 30 minutes — refresh the dashboard snapshot
*/30 * * * * /home/lauchlandupreez/Kingdom/bin/hand snapshot >> /home/lauchlandupreez/Kingdom/.hand-cron.log 2>&1
